<node id="&quot;OPERATING INCOME&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Operating income refers to the revenue generated from Acme Government Solutions' core business activities before accounting for interest and taxes, which reached $100 million due to increased market demand and price changes."&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;"The Operating Income represents Acme Government Solutions' earnings from operations, reflecting its core business activities."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c3ecc13657a59f5d9241c5aa727a07dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0cd6c3e411898f8cfce6a7ad09dc1482</data>
