</node>
<node id="&quot;NET PROFIT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Net profit is the financial gain after all expenses, including operational costs and non-recurring gains or losses, have been deducted from operating income. Acme Government Solutions reported a net profit of $20 million, highlighting effective cost management and profitability."&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;"The Net Profit represents Acme Government Solutions' total earnings after all expenses have been deducted, showcasing its overall profitability."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c3ecc13657a59f5d9241c5aa727a07dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0cd6c3e411898f8cfce6a7ad09dc1482</data>
