</node>
<node id="&quot;TOTAL ASSETS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The Total Assets represent the combined value of everything Acme Government Solutions owns that has monetary value."&lt;SEP&gt;"Total assets represent the sum value of all resources owned by an organization, which for Acme Government Solutions stands at $500 million due to acquisitions, disposals, and revaluations of its asset base."&gt;</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c3ecc13657a59f5d9241c5aa727a07dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0cd6c3e411898f8cfce6a7ad09dc1482</data>
