  <data key="d1">"Shareholder Equity is a financial indicator representing the total value owned by shareholders, indicating ownership interest in Acme Government Solutions."&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;"The Shareholder Equity represents the residual interest in Acme's assets after deducting liabilities, indicating ownership value to shareholders."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-2f44b736ad3c18f059acfe6fabeb81e3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c3ecc13657a59f5d9241c5aa727a07dd</data>
