<node id="&quot;CASH FLOW&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Cash Flow represents the inflow and outflow of cash within an organization, in this case amounting to $50 million for Acme Government Solutions."&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;"The Cash Flow indicates the movement of cash into and out of Acme Government Solutions, crucial for liquidity and operational flexibility."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-2f44b736ad3c18f059acfe6fabeb81e3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c3ecc13657a59f5d9241c5aa727a07dd</data>
