</node>
<node id="&quot;DEBT RATIO&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Debt Ratio is a financial metric showing the proportion of debt used to finance assets, with Acme Government Solutions having a ratio of 0.4."&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;"The Debt Ratio measures Acme's total liabilities against its total assets, indicating leverage and financial risk."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-2f44b736ad3c18f059acfe6fabeb81e3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c3ecc13657a59f5d9241c5aa727a07dd</data>
